â­ Credit Card Fraud Detection System (GUI Based)
ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project is a Machine Learning-based Credit Card Fraud Detection System with a graphical user interface (GUI). It uses a Random Forest Classifier to detect fraudulent transactions using anonymized transaction data.

The system automatically installs required dependencies, trains the model if not already available, and provides both single-transaction and CSV batch prediction options.

